Params: {3: "Vera dodges Gabriel's aerial charge, and slashes at Gabriel's calf with her blade as he zips past her."}
{3: "But Gabriel makes a turn in the air in time, dodging Vera's attack and putting distance between them."}
{3: 'A barrage of air grenades and armor-piercing rounds shower Gabriel continuously, forcing him to retreat before he could attack Vera.'}
{3: "Another explosion follows, and the building above Gabriel's head collapses, interrupting Gabriel's heavy blow."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vera', 3: 'And this is why, big fellas like you are just all muscle... and nothing else.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vera', 3: "Hah, of course! Wringing off your stupid face would take a war the scale of Kowloong. That's not what I can do with my authority.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Noctis', 3: "Aaaalright and done! Asimov's tracker really is something, eh? We now have the full network model of our Gabby here!"}
{3: 'As if to provoke Gabriel, Vera deliberately turns on the speaker to her communications device so that Gabriel can hear the excited Noctis.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vera', 3: "Don't think we didn't catch what Shome's hiding.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vera', 3: "But, it's no different taking it from you.", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Vera arches her body and leaps high in place. Grenades and flashbangs fired by Noctis and No. 21 explode right under her feet.'}
{3: "Gabriel's wings on his back emit a strange glow, and he takes off into the air."}
{2: 'Gabriel', 3: '...This cannot be used for long, but, still enough to catch a mere fly.'}
{3: 'Going after the Vera jumping between buildings, Gabriel soars into the sky.'}
